item.description: Every year, the Washington State Department of Transportation works to reopen State Route 410/Chinook Pass and State Route 123/Cayuse Pass in time for Memorial Day weekend. This year, a washout and the timing of repairs will bring a partial opening.
item.dc:creator: aishad@wsdot.wa.gov

item.title: SR 123/Cayuse Pass scheduled to reopen May 24 and SR 410 Chinook Pass to remain closed
